00:08:10.260 --> 00:08:14.180
♪Words by the western window
hold me captive through the night♪

00:08:16.680 --> 00:08:17.720
(The moment we are bound by oath,)

00:08:19.040 --> 00:08:20.160
(our fates are intertwined.)

00:08:21.840 --> 00:08:23.840
(You no longer stand alone.)

00:08:24.860 --> 00:08:28.740
♪Sorrow etches itself into every word♪

00:08:30.060 --> 00:08:38.940
♪Like a dream too brief, leaving only
the memory of someone I once knew♪

00:08:43.040 --> 00:08:45.720
=Twin Fates=
=End of Episode 9=

00:08:47.320 --> 00:08:51.240
♪In a world of sorrows,
every encounter is fleeting♪

00:08:53.240 --> 00:08:57.120
♪Life is short
but slumber is long on Penglai Island♪

00:08:59.120 --> 00:09:03.640
♪In dreams, mountains and flowers are
as beautiful as jade♪

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:08.920
♪All I ever wish for
is an old friend's return♪

00:09:10.880 --> 00:09:14.720
♪Majestic as a soaring dragon,
veiling the sun with drifting clouds♪

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:20.480
♪Graceful as a flying swan goose,
breaking through snow and peril♪

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:27.440
♪Twenty years forsaken,
I lived the life of an outlaw♪

00:09:28.280 --> 00:09:32.120
♪On the Ximo River,
who was left behind?♪

00:09:32.600 --> 00:09:38.480
♪Bit by bit,
reality shatters my only hope♪

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:44.320
♪Layer by layer, cold blades roll up
the light I once glimpsed in secret♪

00:09:44.320 --> 00:09:47.120
♪Letters have long since yellowed♪

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:50.880
♪Leaving only two lonely lines♪

00:09:51.800 --> 00:09:56.240
♪Even the old yard is covered
with frost♪

00:09:56.240 --> 00:10:01.160
♪Pair after pair,
swallows draw my envious gaze♪

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:07.920
♪Scene after scene,
in dreams I cannot reach♪

00:10:07.920 --> 00:10:10.520
♪While you rest beneath the earth♪

00:10:10.520 --> 00:10:14.120
♪My love lingers in this frosty world♪

00:10:14.920 --> 00:10:22.760
♪How are you now?♪